\]

Using the inclusion-exclusion principle for the three drugs:
\[
P(\text{max} > 8) = 3 \times P(S_i > 8) - 3 \times [P(S_i > 8)]^2 + [P(S_i > 8)]^3
\]
First, compute:
\[
[P(S_i > 8)]^2 = (0.1493083459)^2 = 0.02229298208574
