- \(0 \times 0.25 = 0\)
- \(0.5 \times 0.125 = 0.0625\)
- \(0.75 \times 0.125 = 0.09375\)

Summing these:
\[
0.5 + 0 + 0.0625 + 0.09375 = 0.65625
\]

